<h2 id="이미지-적용">이미지 적용</h2>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>backgound-imge: url(이미지경로);
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="사이즈-조정">사이즈 조정</h2>

<ul>
  <li>%</li>
  <li>cover</li>
  <li>contain</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>background-size: 100%;
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="반복-제어">반복 제어</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>background-repeat:
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="배경속성">배경속성</h2>
<p>*fix</p>
<ul>
  <li>scroll</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>background-attachment: fix
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="위치">위치</h2>

<ul>
  <li>top</li>
  <li>bottom</li>
  <li>left</li>
  <li>right</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>background-position
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>한개 또는 두개의 속성값을 이용하여 위치를 지정할 수 있습니다.</p>

<h2 id="색상">색상</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>backgound-color:
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="backgound">backgound</h2>
<p>여러 속성을 한번에 적용을 할 수도 있습니다.</p>

